The paper discusses the process of knowledge creation, which is a broad topic that can be related to several sub-categories in computer science. However, given the emphasis on online knowledge building portals and the potential use of big data analysis, the most likely sub-categories are natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
